#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.42"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.42:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.42:0.2"
msgid "5. Amatavagga"
msgstr "5. The Deathless"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.42:0.3"
msgid "42. Samudayasutta"
msgstr "42. Origin"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.42:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catunnaṃ, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca desessāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you the origin and the ending of the four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.3"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, kāyassa samudayo?"
msgstr "And what is the origin of the body?"

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.4"
msgid "Āhārasamudayā kāyassa samudayo;"
msgstr "The body originates from food."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.5"
msgid "āhāranirodhā kāyassa atthaṅgamo."
msgstr "When food ceases, the body ends."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.6"
msgid "Phassasamudayā vedanānaṃ samudayo;"
msgstr "Feelings originate from contact."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.7"
msgid "phassanirodhā vedanānaṃ atthaṅgamo."
msgstr "When contact ceases, feelings end."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.8"
msgid "Nāmarūpasamudayā cittassa samudayo;"
msgstr "The mind originates from name and form."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.9"
msgid "nāmarūpanirodhā cittassa atthaṅgamo."
msgstr "When name and form cease, the mind ends."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.10"
msgid "Manasikārasamudayā dhammānaṃ samudayo;"
msgstr "Principles originate from attention."

msgctxt "sn47.42:1.11"
msgid "manasikāranirodhā dhammānaṃ atthaṅgamo”ti."
msgstr "When focus ends, principles end.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.42:1.12"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
